results.description:
The story that inspired SUPREME POWER by J. Michael Straczynski & Gary Frank!
Before WATCHMEN, before KINGDOM COME, before THE AUTHORITY, there was SQUADRON SUPREME, a deconstructionist view of the super-hero paradigm in a real world setting.
